console.log("shaw");


call back hell is one function inside another inside another or another API
, code starts to grow horizontally is called callback hell
It is also known as pyramid of doom
const cart = ["shoes", "pants", "kurta"];
api.createOrder( cart, function() {
function() {
api.proceedToPayment(function() {
api.showOrderSummary{
function() {
api.updateWallet() 
}
}
})
})



